    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow x^2 + y^2 + z^2 - 212x - 416y - 148z + 59300 = 0 \\quad (2)\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      160,
      1095,
      939,
      1143
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nMC = 85 \\Leftrightarrow M \\in (S_3) \\text{ là mặt cầu tâm } C, \\text{ bán kính } R_3 = 85\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
